1. *Pitaj* me zašto sam se sada tu pojavio. (Ask me why I appeared here now.)
2. On me je *pitao* da li mogu da mu pomognem. (He asked me if I can help him.)
3. *Pitano* mi je da li sam spreman da se pridružim. (I was asked if I am ready to join.)
4. *Pitala* sam ga da li zna gde se nalazi. (I asked him if he knows where it is located.)
5. *Pitaju* me da li sam već čuo za to. (They are asking me if I have already heard about that.)